*mew-2.3-r1 (07 Aug 2003)

  13 Sep 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> mew-2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed mandir.  Added cjk IUSE flag to determine whether to install
  Japanese info.  You may need to add (auto-compression-mode) to your
  .emacs file to read Japanese info correctly.

  13 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> mew-2.3-r1.ebuild:
  Marked stable

  07 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> mew-2.3-r1.ebuild,
  files/mew-smtp-2.3-gentoo.patch:
